                        FOREIGN PRESS CENTER SERVICES

                             INT'L INFO PROGRAMS

                         International Press Centers

     International Press Centers have been set up in the following cities
      by local business and civic leaders. They promote the business and
       resources of those cities to local and foreign press. They also
      assist the Foreign Press Centers when they need local contacts and
        information. They broaden and facilitate foreign journalists'
      coverage of the American scene. These IPCs are affiliated with the
                     core For eign Press Center network.

                    International Press Center -- Chicago
